# Images Directory

Struktur folder untuk menyimpan gambar di website Bolehah Corp.

```
images/
├── static/       # Logo, icon, favicon, banner utama
├── portfolios/   # Gambar portfolio/project
├── services/     # Gambar untuk layanan/services
├── testimonials/ # Foto pengguna testimoni
├── team/         # Foto tim/team member
└── blog/         # Gambar artikel blog
```

## Cara Menggunakan di Kode

```tsx
// Tag img biasa
<img src="/images/portfolios/project-1.jpg" alt="Portfolio" />

// Next.js Image component (recommended)
import Image from 'next/image';

<Image
  src="/images/portfolios/project-1.jpg"
  alt="Portfolio"
  width={800}
  height={600}
/>
```
